    dc:creator "Ito, Tomiko; Sasaki, Tetsuro; Takahashi, Chicaco; Sugawara, Hirotaka; Hayashi, Fumio" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "The family Hydroptilidae Curtis (Trichoptera) in the Ogasawara Islands, northwestern Pacific, with particular reference to adaptive radiation in the oceanic islands" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7576781> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7576781>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Phylogenetic trees of six species of Hydroptila endemic to the Ogasawara Islands (H. demersa sp. nov., H. ishiura sp. nov., H. tokoyo sp. nov., H. hahajima sp. nov., H. nagahama sp. nov., and H. ogasawaraensis Ito 2011, in Ito et al. 2011) and the outgroup H. pulchricornis Species Group from mainland Japan (H. phenianica Botosaneanu 1970, H. chinensis Xue & Yang 1990, H. oguranis Kobayashi 1974 and/or H. dampfi Ulmer 1929), based on (2A) 429-bp mitochondrial COI and (2B) 306-bp nuclear 28S sequences. See Table 1 and Fig. 1 for locality of each specimen. The topology is the same between the trees drawn by the neighbor-joining method (NJ) and the maximum likelihood (ML). The numerals at nodes show % bootstrap probabilities in ML (NJ)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7576781/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

